Generate a JSON object with all possible combinations of the following inputs:

Input Name Polos = values [Pique, Long Sleeve, Rugby]  
Input Name Bottom = values [Chinos, Cargo Pants, Utility Pants, Joggers]  
Input Name Jacket = values [Casual, Denim, Leather]  

Each key in the JSON should be formatted as:  
"Polos-Bottom-Jacket": "Style"

Assign the following styles cyclically:  
- Traditional  
- Modern  
- Classy  

Ensure that the order of combinations follows a structured matrix format.
